{"tid":2236188,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台辯稱合約聘利君雅","createTime":"2020-10-09T09:48:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T10:15:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8d5f70c66e85ac9adad4b57f36cb1a2f1098a439","tid":2236188,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:48:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201009/FK33GYSRSRB4NAA2BVEIZCBF4I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201009%2FFK33GYSRSRB4NAA2BVEIZCBF4I%2F&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYznobfi2nm8u4SjNJtTZF4Nk%3D&h=122f876d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201009%2FFK33GYSRSRB4NAA2BVEIZCBF4I%2F&h=56436019\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201009/FK33GYSRSRB4NAA2BVEIZCBF4I/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n港台辯稱合約聘利君雅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eaFjAItMSOkSa7BuuQ7hb-OcVfA=/1775x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EN4QG7MWWRCRJAZKA5I54QFLZI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeaFjAItMSOkSa7BuuQ7hb-OcVfA%3D%2F1775x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEN4QG7MWWRCRJAZKA5I54QFLZI.jpg&h=d87877a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】。。。。。。。。。。。港台節目製作人員工會下周一將就事件舉行員工大會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指過去三年非「試用期」<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。多名員工會上關注管方重啟對利君雅調查的理據及如何「重啟」調查。惟馮在會上只重申不會評論個別個案，又提出利君雅過去三年在港台不是「試用期」，而是「agreement term」（合約期）。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，馮的說法字面上沒有錯，因港台的公務員機制內，只有最低級的節目助理（PA）會有「試用期」，其他公務員職位，例如利君雅所任的助理節目主任，屬於「agreement term」，但實質上兩者性質差不多。<br />\n<br />\n《眾新聞》則引述港台消息人士，指梁家榮在會上雖表明不熟悉公務員的聘任規則，但他及其他監製均質疑針對利君雅的投訴早已完成調查，而她任職港台三年間的六份工作報告亦已作考慮，當局突然重啟調查令人費解，惟馮未有回答。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，港台工會下周一將就事件舉行員工大會，暫未知梁和馮會否出席。"},{"pid":"6993cac4ddc8976abe8099323ed9126aaad2b1b7","tid":2236188,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:50:26.000Z","msg":"咁公墓員嗰3年又叫咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3103b28fdba634a62a7db15e8128261a05b71a12","tid":2236188,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:50:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5192d2ff30c78eebdbfc3462096280aa3e075beb","tid":2236188,"uid":5502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:51:52.000Z","msg":"佢地有約滿酬金，係真係有唔同既"},{"pid":"1b0dc473a2fd049072388976b44cd1eda0984002","tid":2236188,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5192d2ff30c78eebdbfc3462096280aa3e075beb","tid":2236188,"uid":5502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:51:52.000Z","msg":"佢地有約滿酬金，係真係有唔同既"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:55:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />公務員位都合約制有約滿酬金？"},{"pid":"02c885b416e2715d8a715fd377f0fc51020ab12d","tid":2236188,"uid":5502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b0dc473a2fd049072388976b44cd1eda0984002","tid":2236188,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5192d2ff30c78eebdbfc3462096280aa3e075beb","tid":2236188,"uid":5502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:51:52.000Z","msg":"佢地有約滿酬金，係真係有唔同既"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:55:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />公務員位都合約制有約滿酬金？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:57:51.000Z","msg":"港台APO完左頭3年約有總人工15%"},{"pid":"8b0b0aeb7e32101a00dd378b3eaff174b41a7765","tid":2236188,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T10:03:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f122ba8c8c472fff65ade95b5f3e8fc3f7744410","tid":2236188,"uid":74536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02c885b416e2715d8a715fd377f0fc51020ab12d","tid":2236188,"uid":5502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b0dc